    "settings": {
      "code": "<!-- RESULTS REVIEWS SECTION -->\n<section id=\"reference-recenze\" class=\"reference-recenze-section\">\n  <div class=\"reference-recenze-content\">\n    <span class=\"mh-badge\">REVIEWS</span>\n    <h2 class=\"section-title\">What our clients say</h2>\n    <p class=\"section-description\">Read the experiences of our satisfied clients</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"recenze-grid\">\n      <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n        <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Excellent experience from start to finish. Professional approach, great results, and perfect communication. The price was a third less than at Czech clinics. Highly recommend!\"</p>\n        <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n          <div class=\"author-avatar\">JP</div>\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <div class=\"author-name\">Jan P.</div>\n            <div class=\"author-meta\">4500 grafts | DHI method</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n        <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Couldn't be happier. The result is natural and nobody can tell I had a transplant. The support was excellent \u2014 always quick to respond and helped me with everything. Thank you MaxHair!\"</p>\n        <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n          <div class=\"author-avatar\">MK</div>\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <div class=\"author-name\">Martin K.</div>\n            <div class=\"author-meta\">3200 grafts | Sapphire FUE</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n        <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Complete service at a high level. From the airport transfer to post-operative care \u2014 everything perfectly organized. The hotel was luxurious, the doctors professional. Incredible value for the price!\"</p>\n        <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n          <div class=\"author-avatar\">TL</div>\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <div class=\"author-name\">Tom\u00e1\u0161 L.</div>\n            <div class=\"author-meta\">5000 grafts | DHI method</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n        <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"As a woman, I had concerns, but Dr. Merve was amazing. Gentle approach, discreet procedure, and a beautiful natural result. Communication was seamless. I recommend to all women!\"</p>\n        <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n          <div class=\"author-avatar\">KN</div>\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <div class=\"author-name\">Kate\u0159ina N.</div>\n            <div class=\"author-meta\">2800 grafts | Sapphire FUE</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n        <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Beard transplant was the best decision. Finally have a full beard without gaps. The whole process was painless and fast. The price was fair and included everything. MaxHair \u2014 top!\"</p>\n        <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n          <div class=\"author-avatar\">DV</div>\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <div class=\"author-name\">David V.</div>\n            <div class=\"author-meta\">2200 grafts | DHI method</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n        <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"A great investment. Results visible after just 6 months. The team helped me with everything \u2014 from consultation to post-operative care. Czech communication is a huge advantage. Thanks MaxHair!\"</p>\n        <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n          <div class=\"author-avatar\">PH</div>\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <div class=\"author-name\">Petr H.</div>\n            <div class=\"author-meta\">4200 grafts | DHI method</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n        <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Perfect organization of the entire trip. From the first contact to returning home \u2014 everything without problems. The results are great and the price was really favorable. Thank you to the whole team!\"</p>\n        <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n          <div class=\"author-avatar\">JM</div>\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <div class=\"author-name\">Ji\u0159\u00ed M.</div>\n            <div class=\"author-meta\">3600 grafts | Sapphire FUE</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-stars\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605</div>\n        <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Eyebrow transplant changed my life. I finally have natural, thick eyebrows. Dr. Merve was amazing and very precise. The whole process was painless. Highly recommend!\"</p>\n        <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n          <div class=\"author-avatar\">AS</div>\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <div class=\"author-name\">Anna S.</div>\n            <div class=\"author-meta\">Eyebrow transplant</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');\n\n  :root {\n    --primary-gold: #E5C158;\n    --secondary-gold: #D4AF37;\n    --dark-gray: #1A1A1A;\n    --black: #000000;\n    --white: #FFFFFF;\n    --light-gray: #F5F5F5;\n    --medium-gray: #333333;\n  }\n\n  .reference-recenze-section {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    min-height: auto;\n    background: var(--light-gray);\n    padding: 100px 80px;\n  }\n\n  .reference-recenze-content {\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .reference-recenze-section .section-badge,\n  .reference-recenze-section .mh-badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 8px 24px;\n    background: var(--primary-gold) !important;\n    color: #000000 !important;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color: #000000 !important;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n    border-radius: 30px;\n    border: none;\n  }\n\n  .section-title {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n  }\n\n  .section-description {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.7;\n    margin: 0 0 60px 0;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 32px;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-card {\n    background: var(--white);\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    padding: 32px;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-card:hover {\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.2);\n    transform: translateY(-8px);\n  }\n\n  .recenze-stars {\n    font-size: 24px;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-text {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0 0 24px 0;\n    font-style: italic;\n    opacity: 0.85;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-author {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 16px;\n  }\n\n  .author-avatar {\n    width: 56px;\n    height: 56px;\n    background: var(--primary-gold);\n    color: var(--black);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n\n  .author-info {\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n\n  .author-name {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 17px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .author-meta {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: var(--dark-gray);\n    opacity: 0.6;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 1200px) {\n    .recenze-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .reference-recenze-section {\n      padding: 60px 24px;\n    }\n\n    .recenze-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
